message:
Campaigned in Punjab. Addressed a public meeting in Jalandhar in support of Akali Dal & BJP alliance. 

Spoke at length about how the various initiatives of the Central Government have positively impacted the lives of our farmers & youngsters. Black money & corruption adversely impact aspirations of our youth. Assured people that our fight against these two evils will continue. http://nm-4.com/yf4z
